title: Airlines check Boeing 737 engines after fatal Southwest accident
text:
Airlines check Boeing 737 engines after fatal Southwest accident 3:16am IST - 01:32 
Airlines began inspecting Boeing 737 engines after an explosion killed a passenger on a Southwest Airlines flight. Aleksandra Michalska reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
